        "text": "{17} For it is better, if the will of God be so, that ye suffer for well doing, than for evil doing.",
        "children": [
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "cverse3",
            "text": "{17}",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": " For ",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "i",
